  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Move away from violence and allow for peaceful political transition - United Nations Human Rights Council",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United Nations Human Rights Council has emphasized that all security forces, including the military, should respect human rights and act with due restraint, and that all parties should refrain from violence and ensure a peaceful political transition.",
        "Protesters took over the President's House in Colombo last week as the protests that have erupted nationwide as a result of the severe economic crisis have gradually intensified.",
        "After that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa had announced his resignation on the 13th, but he left the country yesterday.",
        "Protests were already being carried out demanding that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe also step down, and in the background of his house being set on fire a few days ago, the protests against him who took over as acting president got stronger yesterday.",
        "In such a background, it has been stated in the official Twitter account of the United Nations Human Rights Council that:",
        "We urge all parties in Sri Lanka to refrain from violence and ensure a peaceful political transition. In the current situation, a mechanism that is inclusive and respectful of the rule of law is essential.",
        "We also request respect for life and property. The report emphasized that all security forces, including the military, should respect human rights and act with due restraint."
      ],
